; *** In this file, the default deictic reference of some terms;
;     Currently, the only example is "the city", which is fixed to "Torino".
;     This should be made context-dependent; if HOPS is used in Barcelona, then
;     "the city" should refer to Barcelona!
(setq *DEICTIC-REFERENCE*
   '(
      (££city £Torino)
      (££moment £now)
      (££day-descr %neutral)
          ; *** the previous one is for "this monday",  "this saturday",
          ;     where "this monday" is interpreted the same as "monday"
    ))
